title: Alilang Silver Golden Tone Crystal Rhinestone Peacock Feather Dangle Drop Vintage Inspired Earrings
features: REFINED, YET STYLISH. These chic earrings are anything but basic. The gold toned metal is delicately curved and shaped into a feather-like design. The large, dark center stone is similar to the eye of a peacock's tail feather.

ELEGANT GOLD EARRING COLORS. The deep colored center stone is set firmly, surrounded by a beautiful golden tone metal. These dangling earrings drop from a hook, giving a little bit of movement to your outfit.

GREAT FOR DAY OR NIGHT. Wear this fashionable jewelry with any part of your wardrobe. Subtle enough to wear to work, but glam enough to wear to a party, banquet, or ball! These dangle earrings are the versatile piece your jewelry box needs.
BEAUTIFULLY PACKAGED - Most of our jewelry arrives in a complimentary Alilang gift box, while bigger pieces are packed in elegant organza bags making them ready to gift for loved ones.
description: Show off with these Alilang earrings! Inspired by the natural beauty of the incredible peacock, these earrings add just the right amount of both elegance and fun to any outfit you are wearing. Chic, yet trendy, they can be worn with everyday clothes, or be the perfect addition to a formal outfit. These Alilang feathered peacock earrings are just what any fashionista's jewelry box needs!
